<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下為樓主未看,但網上好評少伏之作<br />\n注:有(括號)即作者之作品皆出色,請自行GOOGLE作者名看其餘作品簡介<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">網上好評</span></strong></div></span><br />\n數據封神 <br />\n網遊之金庸奇俠傳<br />\n雪中悍刀行<br />\n回到過去變成貓(陳詞懶調)<br />\n星級獵人<br />\n無限殘說(黑籍)<br />\n逆鱗<br />\n龍印戰神(半步滄桑)<br />\n超級基因優化液</blockquote><br />\n求其打住先,發現太高難度<br />\n主要係我都唔記得自己睇過咩書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒試下整理埋上一個貼既巴打分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47abb1819af1c4be4ec87d4e2d2e5cf9cc37ce12","tid":417553,"uid":144718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T19:15:34.000Z","msg":"推介 美女請留步 <br />\n殺手房東俏房東第二部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52fee2b1997ab25453662e28c9829766ecef101","tid":417553,"uid":144718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T19:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推介 美女請留步 <br />\n殺手房東俏房東第二部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲網會改做 巔峰強少 作者:老施"},{"pid":"ac898cb92deaa8aea17acee768c15c29d569a04f","tid":417553,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T19:24:48.000Z","msg":"有冇d類似全職法師 唔想用腦淨係想爽下就算"},{"pid":"b11b123331885e07fcde47876c9585f613f2b9e2","tid":417553,"uid":146032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:50:33.000Z","msg":"推介下唔係上面張list度既書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">個人認為係好書</span></span><br />\n<br />\n恐怖靈異<br />\n青葉靈異事務所(未完<br />\n食咒三部曲{<br />\n食咒<br />\n陰陽食譜(未完,年頭無啦啦比人封左,好似最近會出返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n通靈美食家(新開未完)<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n科幻<br />\n修真四萬年<br />\n<br />\n玄幻<br />\n史上第一祖師爺<br />\n史上最強師兄(未完)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">兩本都同作者既爽文,但唔會無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n走進修仙(可以當做修仙版奧術神座,但係呢本玩埋以前既科學家落去,而且科學既資識拓展得較闊而偏向描寫於數學方面)<br />\n<br />\n魔幻<br />\n寂靜王冠(中意音樂既推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n罪域的骨終為王(穿越作,琥珀之劍及帶點dark soul式的背景)<br />\n<br />\n特拉福買家俱樂部(呢本個人認為睇既唔係主角點無敵,而係一個個顧客的故事,感情細節描述得幾有代入感,有感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n無腦爽文<br />\n英雄監獄<br />\n惡魔囚籠"},{"pid":"98e5b0138b91ac21a36a74fa4954158d27392c63","tid":417553,"uid":142428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:28:23.000Z","msg":"留名 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7511818a86915b866d9e82adb595e9accea33925","tid":417553,"uid":147445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:46:50.000Z","msg":"終於有4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb892db1b9e57af6e6205f22622e853e00b487c","tid":417553,"uid":34604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:29:26.000Z","msg":"留名 本來見唔到都想開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c75799ce165735da6716b5fb573eb0c7b97eb2","tid":417553,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T17:15:35.000Z","msg"